strategies: I just read each name carefully and thought of the different states associated with the cities
familiar: Whether or not I knew that city had existed; either from hearing things about it; or if I had visited it.
memorable: I ranked some unique sounding cities as being more memorable; but I also ranked the cities that I have visited as memorable as well.
unique: I ranked uniqueness based on whether I have heard the name before; and whether or not there are multiple cities/towns using that same name. I also considered whether or not the names were basic; or more creative.
realistic: I ranked this mostly based on whether or not I knew the city existed; or if i can imagine it being the real name of a city.
